.","footer-uk-link-text":"Switch to Octopus Energy UK.","footer-ev-cta":"For EV questions, call","footer-days-text":"9 a.m. -5 p.m. on Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday, Friday and 9 a.m. - 4 p.m. on Thursday, CT","footer-outage-text":"Outage Information","footer-complaints-text":"For complaints, email","footer-texas-proud-text":"Proudly made in Texas.","footer-rights-text":"All Rights Reserved","accounts":"Accounts","accountOverview":"Overview","back":"Back","errorEmail":"Email: heretohelp@octopusenergy.com","processing":"Processing","submit":"Submit","verify":"Verify","amount":"Amount","negativeBalance":"This is the amount owed to Octopus Energy","zeroBalance":"You’re all caught up!","positiveBalance":"You’ve got credit in your account! This will be applied to your next bill, automatically.","button_signIn":"Sign in","button_dashboard":"Dashboard","button_signOut":"Sign out","creditCardHeader":"Credit Card Details","secureTransaction":"All transactions are safe and secure","add_promo_code":"Add a promo/referral code","enter_zipcode":"Enter a zip code","zipcode":"Zip code","plans_zipcode_modal":"Plans available in your area","plans_referral_modal":"Save even more!","emailHelp":"heretohelp@octopusenergy.com","dismiss":"DISMISS","downloadApp":"For a better mobile experience, download our free app!","view":"View","octopusEnergyApp":"Octopus Energy App","press":"Press"},"paymentGateway":{"apiKeyExpired":"An error occurred while processing your card. Please contact us for assistance (833) OCTO-888.","cardDeclinedError":"Your card was declined.","cardInsufficientFundsError":"Your card has insufficient funds.","cardExpiredError":"Your card has expired.","cardIncorrectSecurityCodeError":"Your card's security code is incorrect.","cardProcessingError":"An error occurred while processing your card. Try again in a little bit.","cardInvalidNumberError":"Your card number is invalid.","accountNumberInvalid":"Invalid account number. Please check your entry.","routingNumberInvalid":"Invalid routing number. Please check your entry.","verificationError":"We are unable to verify your payment. Please check your entries.","maxPaymentMethodsError":"Maximum payment methods error. Please contact us for assistance (833) OCTO-888.","incorrectAddress":"Invalid address. Please check your entry.","incorrectZip":"Invalid zip. Please check your entry."},"enrollment/products/octoPlus12":{"cardSubhead":"/month based on average monthly usage of 1,000 kWh","description1":"Lock in your rate for 12 months and enjoy excellent long-term value, billed monthly, with a $100 early termination fee.","description2":"A credit check and/or deposit may apply. Intelligent Octopus Conditions may apply.","card_bullet_1":"12-month locked-in rate","card_bullet_2":"Monthly bill","card_bullet_3":"Save $25 with Intelligent Octopus","card_bullet_4":"Always green","modal_subtext_2":"PLAN_PLACEHOLDER gives you long-term value, with no hassle monthly billing, with a $100 early termination fee. You’ll get a great, fixed rate for 12 months, powered by 100% renewable energy, generated right here in Texas.","summary1":"12-Month Locked-In Rate","details1":"Long-term value, all year long.","summary2":"No Bait and Switch","details2":"When your 12 month plan is up, you'll roll onto our Month-to-Month plan with variable pricing if you have not renewed your fixed rate plan by the expiration date. Don't worry, we'll give you a head up when it's time to choose a new plan!","summary3":"No Hidden Fees","details3":"We’re completely forthcoming with what you’re paying for and why. No tricks here, what you see is what you get.","summary4":"100% Renewable Energy","details4":"We want to make the eco‐friendly choice the easy choice, so all of our rates use 100% green electricity — and they’re no more expensive than our competitors’ non‐green rates.","summary5":"Why $10 Per Month?","details5":"This $10 monthly fee allows us to keep our rates super low and ensure the incredible service our customers are used to! Nearly all energy providers charge a monthly base fee, but most choose to hide it in their EFLs — we’re letting you know what everything costs, upfront. Honesty is always the best policy.","summary6":"Have solar panels on your home?","details6":"When your panels produce more than you need — meaning more than what it takes to power your home — your two-way electricity meter will send the excess power to the grid. We then buy back whatever you’ve sent to the grid at the current wholesale market price in real time. Whatever the market rate for power is, that’s what we will credit you — no caps, and you can roll over credits indefinitely! And, if you ever leave our supply (we’re really hoping you’ll stick around), we’ll cash out any unused credits.","ioSave":"Save more with Intelligent Octopus","ioSaveThermostatDetails":"When you connect your smart thermostat to Intelligent Octopus you unlock even more energy savings every month. Learn more about Intelligent Octopus ","ioConditions":"Intelligent Octopus Conditions may apply.","ioSaveEVDetails":"Unlock more energy savings when you pair your EV to Intelligent Octopus smart charging. You just tell us when and we’ll optimize your charging to the very greenest of times. Learn more about Intelligent Octopus ","ioAdditionalSavings":"Unlock a lower rate with Intelligent Octopus","ioAdditionalSavingsDetails":"Save even more on your energy bill when you connect your smart devices to Intelligent Octopus. Currently works with thermostats, EVs, and batteries. Learn more about our Smart Features "},"enrollment/products/octoPlus24":{"cardSubhead":"/month based on average monthly usage of 1,000 kWh","card_bullet_1":"24-month locked-in rate","card_bullet_2":"Monthly bill","card_bullet_3":"No cancellation fees","card_bullet_4":"Always green","modal_subtext_1":"Introducing our first 24-month plan!","modal_subtext_2":"Worry less about your energy by locking in your rate for the next 24-months with easy monthly billing. Get on with your day and know that we’ve got you covered. A completely fixed rate for 24 months, powered by 100% renewable energy from Texas.","modal_pt_1_head":"24-Month Locked-In Rate","modal_pt_1_body":"Locked-in for two years, incredible long-term value.","modal_pt_2_head":"No Bait and Switch","modal_pt_2_body":"When 24 months are up, you’ll be rolled onto our month-to-month plan, which won’t be that different from the rate you have now and you can easily renew onto any of our plans — just give us a call. We’ll also give you a heads up when that renewable date is coming up!","modal_pt_3_head":"No Hidden Fees","modal_pt_3_body":"We’re completely forthcoming with what you’re paying for and why. No tricks here, what you see is what you get.","modal_pt_4_head":"100% Renewable Energy","modal_pt_4_body":"We want to make the eco‐friendly choice the easy choice, so all of our rates use 100% green electricity — and they’re no more expensive than our competitors’ non‐green rates.","modal_pt_5_head":"Why $10 Per Month?","modal_pt_5_body":"This $10 monthly fee allows us to keep our rates super low and ensure the incredible service our customers are used to! Nearly all energy providers charge a monthly base fee, but most choose to hide it in their EFLs — we’re letting you know what everything costs, upfront. Honesty is always the best policy.","modal_pt_6_head":"Have solar panels on your home?","modal_pt_6_body":"When your panels produce more than you need — meaning more than what it takes to power your home — your two-way electricity meter will send the excess power to the grid. We then buy back whatever you’ve sent to the grid at the current wholesale market price in real time. Whatever the market rate for power is, that’s what we will credit you — no caps, and you can roll over credits indefinitely! And, if you ever leave our supply (we’re really hoping you’ll stick around), we’ll cash out any unused credits."},"enrollment/products/octoPlus36":{"cardSubhead":"/month based on average monthly usage of 1,000 kWh","description1":"A worry-free, 36-month rate with incredible long-term value, billed monthly, with $175 early termination fee.","description2":"A credit check and/or deposit may apply.","card_bullet_1":"36-month locked-in rate","card_bullet_2":"Monthly bill","card_bullet_3":"Always green","modal_subtext_1":"A locked-in rate for three whole years?","modal_subtext_2":"Plan ahead with a great fixed rate and know you’re set for years to come. You lock in your rate for 36 months, with our easy monthly billing, powered by 100% renewable energy, right here in Texas.","summary1":"36-Month Locked-In Rate","details1":"Three years of an excellent rate, our longest plan yet!","summary2":"No Bait and Switch","details2":"When 36 months are up, you’ll be rolled onto our month-to-month plan, which won’t be that different from the rate you have now and you can easily renew onto any of our plans — just give us a call. We’ll also give you a heads up when that renewable date is coming up!","summary3":"No Hidden Fees","details3":"We’re completely forthcoming with what you’re paying for and why. No tricks here, what you see is what you get.","summary4":"100% Renewable Energy","details4":"We want to make the eco‐friendly choice the easy choice, so all of our rates use 100% green electricity — and they’re no more expensive than our competitors’ non‐green rates.","summary5":"Why $10 Per Month?","details5":"This $10 monthly fee allows us to keep our rates super low and ensure the incredible service our customers are used to! Nearly all energy providers charge a monthly base fee, but most choose to hide it in their EFLs — we’re letting you know what everything costs, upfront. Honesty is always the best policy.","summary6":"Have solar panels on your home?","details6":"When your panels produce more than you need — meaning more than what it takes to power your home — your two-way electricity meter will send the excess power to the grid. We then buy back whatever you’ve sent to 