":"Due to the current volatility in the energy market we are not currently accepting new customers. Please check back soon!","enrollmentsUpSoon":"Hello, our enrollment is offline right now, but will be back up shortly! In the meantime, sign up on our waitlist 👇","enrollmentsOutageNeedToKnow":"You need to know this","enrollmentsOutageEmailPrompt":"Would you like an email when prices fall?","enrollmentsOutageEmailButton":"Yes, please email me","accountNumberInfoPrompt":"Your Octopus Energy account number:","phoneNumber":"Phone number","depositDeclinedErrorMessage":"Unfortunately, your recent deposit was declined. Please give us a call at (833) 628-6888 to complete your enrollment.","pricesChangedDuringEnrollment":"Oh no! It looks like we updated prices while you were enrolling. We will happily honor the lowest rate, so please contact us at heretohelp@octopus.energy.com to confirm.","successThankYouParagraph":"Hooray! Your account has been set up and your switch is underway. Typically, your data will be available in your account within a few hours, but it may take up to 48 hours.","successVerification":"Your account has been verified!","verificationError":"It looks like we encountered an error while verifying your account.","verificationErrorContact":"If you would like to continue your enrollment, please contact our team at","enrollmentDataError":"To continue enrollment, please speak with one of our Energy Specialists by calling (833) OCTO-888, 9 a.m. -5 p.m. on Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday, Friday and 9 a.m. - 4 p.m. on Thursday, CT.","navigatorSkipPayment":"I will add a payment method in the future.*","navigatorSkipPaymentDisclaimer":"A payment method will need to be added in order to complete your service transfer.","declinedButAllowedToContinue":"Your payment has not been processed. One of our Energy Specialists will reach out to you shortly to continue your enrollment process.","successIOSubtitle":"Own an ecobee or Sensi thermostat?","successIOStep1_1":"Log in","here":"here","successIOStep1_2":"FYI your username is the same email you used to sign up with us.","successIOStep2_1":"Once you’re logged in select","successIOStep2_2":"Connect your device.","successIOStep3_1":"Need more help connecting? Check out our","successIOStep3_2":"for more info.","aep_delay":"Please allow 2-5 days for AEP to process your move in/switch.","serviceSwitchDateMoreInfoTitle":"Good to know:","serviceSwitchDateMoreInfoBody":"We try to get you switched same day if requested, but please note: It can take up to 72 hours."},"enrollment/plans":{"title":"Octopus Energy - Our Plans","zipCode_heading":"Plans available in your zip code:","serviceProvider_text":"Service Provider:","locationToggle_text":"Change Location","planToggle_heading":"Choose your plan","billingType_monthly":"Monthly Billing","billingType_payg":"Pay-As-You-Go","zipCode_placeholder":"Enter a Zipcode","zipCode_buttonCta":"Start My Quote","zipCode_notice":"Enter your zip code to find out how much you can save.","multipleProviders_text":"There are multiple service providers in your zip code. Your actual rate will be determined during enrollment.","prime_category_head":"Limited-time offer!","prime_category_head2":"Monthly Billing Plans that have a little extra:","innovativePlansTitle1":"Want to save even more with our most innovative plans?","innovativePlansTitle2":"Specialized rates that help balance the grid.","renewable_text":"All of our plans use 100% renewable energy, generated right here in Texas!","filter_prompt":"Let's help you find your perfect plan:","filter_all":"All","filter_promotions":"Promotions","filter_pay_as_you_go":"Pay as you go","filter_no_credit_check":"No credit check","filter_ev":"I own an EV","filter_long_term":"Long term","filter_no_termination_fees":"No termination fees","filter_solar":"Solar","plans_available_zipcode":"Plans available for your zip code","plans_available_tdsp":"Plans available for your area","plans_available_esi":"Plans available for your ESI ID","payAsYouGo":"Pay as you go","monthly":"Monthly","chooseYourRate":"Choose your rate","calculatedAverageSpending":"We've calculated the average of what you would spend each month.","willVary":"This will vary if you use more or less energy than estimated.","serviceProviderTDU":"Transmission and Distribution Utility (TDU) corresponding to your address.","navigator_title":"Switching only takes a few simple steps.","navigator_step1":"Speak with our Brand Ambassador","navigator_step2":"Compare your latest bill","navigator_step3":"Switch \u0026 save!","navigator_getStarted_head":"Let's get started.","navigator_getStarted_subHead":"What's your zip code?","navigator_zipCode_form_field_cta":"Get a quote"},"marketing/homepage":{"pageTitle1":"Smarter Energy.","pageTitle2":"Fairer Rates.","zipCodeCta":"Enter your zip code for rates in your area:","zipCodeButton":"See Quotes","descriptionSectionTitle1":"Consistently fair rates.","descriptionSectionBody1":"Transparent fair pricing for the long-term not just the fixed term.","descriptionSectionTitle2":"Exceptional customer service.","descriptionSectionBody2":"Fast friendly responses that make dealing with us a breeze.","descriptionSectionTitle3":"100% green rates.","descriptionSectionBody3":"We’re powered by local renewable energy sources like wind and solar.","ratingsHeading":"Rated 5 stars for excellent customer service","solarTitle":"Interested in solar?","solarHeading":"Generate your own energy, right at home.","solarBody":"Learn more about our solar buy-back program or get in touch for a free solar consultation.","solarCta":"Learn more","switchingTitle":"Making it simple","switchingHeading":"Switching has never been easier.","switchingBody1":"Same-day switching available","switchingBody2":"No disruption to your electricity supply","switchingBody3":"We’ll inform your old electric retailer","switchingBody4":"Award-winning customer service","blogTitle":"Our wider community.","blogHeading":"The latest from the Octoverse","blogCta":"Visit our blog","featuredInTitle":"Don’t take our word for it.","featuredInHeading":"As featured in…","featuredInQuote1":"Octopus Energy’s American Dream is fast becoming real","featuredInQuote2":"Octopus Energy US launching leasing program for EVs, demand-response energy plan","featuredInQuote3":"Big hurdles on the road to moving millions of U.S. drivers into EVs","featuredInQuote4":"2022 Fire Awards: 4 top energy innovators","featuredInQuote5":"Energy company with U.S. HQ in Houston acquires local business","featuredInQuote6":"Rethinking the future of refueling","smartFeaturesHeader":"Unlock the cheapest rates with smart features","smartFeaturesCardTitle1":"Intelligent Octopus for thermostats","smartFeaturesCardDescription1-1":"We optimize your temperature settings, ","smartFeaturesCardDescription1-2":"you save $300+ per year","smartFeaturesCardDescription1-3":". Add your thermostat to ","smartFeaturesCardDescription1-4":"Intelligent Octopus","smartFeaturesCardDescription1-5":" in the app.","smartFeaturesCardTitle2":"Intelligent Octopus for EVs","smartFeaturesCardDescription2-1":"We smart schedule your EV charging, ","smartFeaturesCardDescription2-2":"you get up to 30% off your rate","smartFeaturesCardDescription2-3":". Add your EV to ","smartFeaturesCardDescription2-4":"Intelligent Octopus","smartFeaturesCardDescription2-5":" in the app.","smartFeaturesCardTitle3":"Fan Club","smartFeaturesCardDescription3-1":"No EV or smart thermostat? ","smartFeaturesCardDescription3-2":"You can still get a discounted rate when wind turbines are spinning in Texas. Savings that blow, in a good way.","smartFeaturesCardActionButton":"Learn more","smartFeaturesSubtext":"Save hundreds per year with innovative add-ons for smart thermostats, EVs, home batteries and solar.","smartFeaturesCTA":"Browse smart features","aboutUsTitle1":"More about us","aboutUsTitle2":"We're more than just an energy company","aboutUsContent1":"Hi, we're Octopus Energy. We're a global energy company with an unstoppable mission to bring renewable energy and tech-driven solutions to the masses without breaking the bank. We offer smart-energy plans in Texas for any budget because we believe good energy shouldn't cost the earth or your wallet. Our 100% transparent, fixed-rate plans are simple to understand and don't require you to jump through hoops just to get the lowest price possible.","aboutUsContent2":"If you own an electric vehicle (EV), smart thermostat, or have a home battery, you can save even more with one of the cheapest rates in Texas when you connect your smart devices to Intelligent Octopus. Smart devices = bigger discounts.","aboutUsContent3":"If you have rays for days and own solar panels, you can earn solar buyback credits at the wholesale rate with no caps, or expiration dates, and cash out after $50 with one of Texas' best solar buyback programs.","aboutUsContent4":"Don't walk, run to join us today and be part of something awesome."},"marketing/navigatorLandingPage":{"title":"Join Octopus Energy","header_h1":"Switch to an energy company you can trust with fair and transparent pricing.","plan_content":"We offer great long-term value plans depending on where you live.","where_you_live":"depending on where you live.","header_FindPlan":"Find the plan that's right for you","subHead_GreatValueLongTerm":"Great value for the long term, not just the fixed term.","subHead_GreatValueLongTerm_Content":"We love our customers. That’s why we’re committed to providing fairly-priced energy and outstanding customer service for everyone in Texas. Did we mention we’re also 100% green? Good for the planet, good for your wallet, and good for the soul.","whyChooseOctopus_Button":"Why choose Octopus Energy?","subHead_Switching":"Switching has never been easier","subHead_Switching_ThreeWays":"Three ways we make it simple.","subHead_Switching_ThreeWays_1":"Same-day switching","subHead_Switching_ThreeWays_2":"No disruption to your electricity supply","subHead_Switching_ThreeWays_3":"We’ll inform your old electric retailer","subHead_Ready":"We’re ready for our close-up","subHead_Ready_Content":"As featured in…","howMuchSave_Button":"See how much you can save!"},"marketing/404":{"subHead":"Sorry, we can't find that page","backLink":"Back to Homepage"},"product/productCard":{"per":"per","rate":"energy rate of","month":"month","averageMonthlyUse":"based on average monthly usage of 1,000 kWh","lockedInRate":"locked-in rate","solarBuyback":"Solar buyback","solarBuyBackTooltip":"Our solar buyback rate follows the wholesale market. High demand on the grid means a high export rate.","ioSavings":"Save $25 on your monthly bill by connecting your ecobee thermostat with Intelligent Octopus.","allPaperless":"No fuss, all paperless comms!","earlyTerminationFee":"$100 Early Termination Fee","startButton":"Get started now","waitlistLink":"More than 90 days out? We'll remind you when to switch.","selectProduct":"Select this plan","moreInfo":"Learn more about this plan","yourRights":"Your Rights as a Customer","serviceTerms":"Terms of Service","prepaidDisclosureNotice":"Prepaid Disclosure Notice","documentsTitle":"Plan Documents","getQuote":"Get a quote","ratesStartingAt":"rates starting at","renewable":"renewable","prepaidDisclosureStatement":"Prepaid Disclosure Notice","here":"here","rateInfo":"Rate info","onlyTesla":"This offer is only compatible with Audi, BMW, Ford, Jaguar, Mini, Porsche, Tesla, and VW EVs. More models will be available soon.","compatibleOnlyList":"This offer is only compatible with Amazon, ecobee, Honeywell, and Sensi thermostats right now. More models will be available soon.","hundredPercentRenewable":"100% renewable","electricity":"electricity","baitAndSwitch":"No bait and switch","monthlyEstimate":"Monthly estimate - including fees","basedOnAverage":"Based on average monthly usage of 1,000 kWh","unitCost":"Unit cost","withThermostat":"with connected thermostat","withEV":"with connected EV","teslaCompatible":"Compatible with most EVs","compatibleThermostats":"Compatible with Amazon, ecobee, Honeywell, and Sensi.","checkYourInboxThermostat":"Check your inbox after sign-up for instructions on how to set up your thermostat.","checkYourInboxEV":"Check your inbox after sign-up for instructions on how to set up your EV.","yourPlan":"Your Plan","forFirstMonth":"for the first month","rateChangesMonthly":"Rate changes monthly","onMTM":"On Month-to-Month,","priceNotLocked":"your price isn't locked in. It changes every month","basedOnWholesale":"based on the wholesale cost of energy.","youWillStayUntil":"You'll stay on this until you choose another plan. You can leave any time without termination fees.","wantSecurity":"Want the security of a fixed plan? Look at Octo12 or OctoPrepay12.","autopay":"Autopay required","ioThermostatAgreementTitle":"Connect your smart thermostat after signing up in order to keep this discounted rate.","ioThermostatAgreementCheckboxLabel":"I have a Sensi or ecobee thermostat device and I will connect it to Intelligent Octopus. I understand that if I don’t connect my device I’ll be switched over to the standard Octo 12 rate and the discounted rate will not be applied.","ioThermostatAgreementDescriptionSubtitle":"Don’t have a compatible thermostat?","ioThermostatAgreementDescriptionText":"Sign up to our standard Octo 12 plan. You can connect to Intelligent Octopus once you have an eligible device, at any time.","ioEVAgreementTitle":"Connect your electric vehicle after signing up in order to keep this discounted rate.","ioEVAgreementCheckboxLabel":"I will connect my car to Intelligent Octopus. I understand that if I don’t connect my device I’ll be switched over to the standard Octo 12 rate and the discounted rate will not be applied.","ioEVAgreementDescriptionSubtitle":"Compatible with:","ioEVAgreementDescriptionText":"Tesla, Audi, BMW, Mini, Porsche, Jaguar, some Volkswagen and Ford. If you don’t find your car make","ioContactUs":"let us know here.","ioAgreementSubmit":"Sign me up","ioAgreementCancel":"Back to rates"},"signup":{"header":"Get notified when we arrive!","form_title":"Yes! Let me know when I can sign up for Octopus Energy.","signup":"Sign up","email_match":"Emails must match","field_required":"This field is required","exposure_via":"How did you learn about Octopus Energy?","confirm_email":"Confirm email","email_not_entered":"Confirm email is required","signup_successful":"You have successfully signed up for notification when we arrive in your area!","signup_error":"Sorry, we are unable to sign you up for notification at this time."},"enrollment/banner":{"enrollment1":"Almost done!","enrollment2":"Just a few details left.","ecobeeHome":"Finish signing up to Octo 12 with thermostat to get your FREE ecobee + $25 a month","ecobeeSuccess":"Thank you for joining Octopus Energy! We will email you within 24 hours to get you set up with your new free ecobee thermostat. If you have any questions in the meantime, please email us at heretohelp@octopusenergy.com or give us a call at 833-628-6888.","fanClubHome1":"Join Octopus Energy to become a member of our Fan Club!","fanClubHome2":"Just enter your zip code to get started.","fanClubSuccess1":"Thanks for joining Octopus Energy and welcome to","fanClubSuccess2":"The Fan Club! 🎉","directMailOfferHome1":"Let's make it official! 🎉 Your $50 credit will be applied to your account after you've enrolled with us.","directMailOfferHome2":"Just enter your zip code to get started.","directMailOfferSuccess":"Thanks for joining Octopus Energy! Your $50 credit will be applied to your account before your first bill.","directMailNoOfferHome1":"Let's make it official! 🎉","directMailNoOfferHome2":"Just enter your zip code to get started.","directMailNoOfferSuccess":"Thanks for joining Octopus Energy! 🐙 ⚡"}}},"page":"/efl","query":{"lang":"en","service-provider":"ONCOR","id":"176","nextInternalLocale":"en"},"buildId":"hYI8SbE-jaLUj9eVDgah_","isFallback":false,"isExperimentalCompile":true,"appGip":true,"locale":"en","locales":["en","es"],"defaultLocale":"en","scriptLoader":[]}</script></body></html>